{"tid":831213,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[已變質] 華御結啲飯團最近變得好撚難食","createTime":"2018-09-21T17:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T13:21:10.000Z","uid":194606,"like":409,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7da82b6eb732129a526738e8a50ed985813f75","tid":831213,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:34:50.000Z","msg":"呢間本來都算係數一數二最好味嘅一間飯團公司<br />\n雖然係貴咗啲，但係都值得買，不過而家真係買唔落<br />\n<br />\n自從上幾個禮拜開始，我喺太古康怡嗰間鋪頭度買過一個飯團食，個包裝竟然好難拆之後啲紫菜又淋，入面啲飯又散又硬又乾，完全係失曬水準。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁我就畀多次機會佢，就喺前日柴灣嗰間買咗個三文魚飯團，屌你有冇搞錯仲係咁難食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢哋係轉咗廚房，用咗啲平價嘅師傅，再繼續以高價賣出，咁又可以賺多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死奸商 以後都唔撚幫襯你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n請問有冇同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edff0fa959a33e0b0f8fed629c4e5db3b1b66f10","tid":831213,"uid":21423,"like":128,"dislike":10,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a42b3f347049aaeb4a46c56ef8a09f38f1c001ba","tid":831213,"uid":198583,"like":205,"dislike":40,"score":165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"飯一嚿都畀咁撚多錢買 死戇鳩"},{"pid":"360503fc214dd338b1f97da3f6aab7f09d997b38","tid":831213,"uid":194606,"like":4,"dislike":47,"score":-43,"quote":{"pid":"a42b3f347049aaeb4a46c56ef8a09f38f1c001ba","tid":831213,"uid":198583,"like":205,"dislike":40,"score":165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"飯一嚿都畀咁撚多錢買 死戇鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"咁有時買幾嚿又可以當一餐lunch呀嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快靚正<br />\n不過而家... 收皮啦"},{"pid":"cbdd06de34e0c173658ffba45745c5cbbc3293df","tid":831213,"uid":55614,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:42:18.000Z","m